{"tid":2304049,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"自反修例運動潛水一年 新歌講和諧疑轉軚  Supper Moment被批離地搖滾叛徒","createTime":"2020-11-28T12:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T08:19:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b544a9a103f0141aa3ed1f2ff0ca169806a8b32f","tid":2304049,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201128/EKJM5CJZHZBL3AAU62VLBKVIUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201128%2FEKJM5CJZHZBL3AAU62VLBKVIUQ%2F&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR3za4IX%2BHJq2V8VgSm%2B5QfQ%3D&h=f8223248\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201128%2FEKJM5CJZHZBL3AAU62VLBKVIUQ%2F&h=5e5b76ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201128/EKJM5CJZHZBL3AAU62VLBKVIUQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n自反修例運動潛水一年 新歌講和諧疑轉軚 <br />\nSupper Moment被批離地搖滾叛徒<br />\n<br />\n樂隊Supper Moment（SM）組成14年，近年人氣急升，2013年因唱反國教歌，更被不少人視為香港有態度樂隊，上年反修例運動遊行時，更會播出他們的成名作《無盡》。不過近日有網民不滿眾成員潛水沒有發聲表態，至日前於網上開演唱會唱出大碟中所有新作，其中不但有國語歌，當中更宣揚大愛包容及和諧，因而被指無視港人的痛，態度落差之大有轉軚嫌疑，網民失望指摘：「搖滾叛徒！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【毋忘初衷】樂隊奮抗強權紛表態<br />\n<br />\n四人樂隊Supper Moment被視為有理想有態度的本地樂隊，近年甚受歡迎，並於本周二（24日）舉行網上音樂會，在約50分鐘內全數唱出新專輯《Everything Is You》內13首歌曲。樂隊久未推出新作，歌迷以期待心情觀看，卻發現當中不但有三首國語歌，而且歌詞內容都宣揚大愛講和諧、叫人包容，與過往堅持抱負對抗強權的歌詞截然不同，似有轉軚嫌疑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n1V5Lx_fxHUG58nGmR5gozppi3U=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WH5A2SCXNRD2HMQOAPW7SLWZK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn1V5Lx_fxHUG58nGmR5gozppi3U%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWH5A2SCXNRD2HMQOAPW7SLWZK4.jpg&h=33081d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■2018年Supper Moment於香港亞洲流行音樂節跟特首林鄭月娥的一張合照，惹來不少網民狂轟。 互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uJBuXWIFNF14LIWCwCRtGx4IYj0=/856x851/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/72CP6GOMNRDMLCTMKP4LSHMCLI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuJBuXWIFNF14LIWCwCRtGx4IYj0%3D%2F856x851%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F72CP6GOMNRDMLCTMKP4LSHMCLI.gif&h=33a6b42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有不少「濕爬」fans於網上力撐偶像，但更多是fans對他們失望的留言。互聯網圖片"},{"pid":"c0f962c3b37efd615191279d9aa09101105e80f4","tid":2304049,"uid":183576,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0d3791e323664e7c753562a1c9ccf371972381","tid":2304049,"uid":100775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:44:54.000Z","msg":"應該會改名做內地歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbd057ab6f49b49bda029f0414bd25e3eb90822","tid":2304049,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"連衛兵又衝出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過算啦呢隊野都唔關我事搏盡無悔嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc556fdb57ff60c6d73b08dc34279c5ec06a2aa2","tid":2304049,"uid":286209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T13:20:06.000Z","msg":"進軍支那市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283c18485aeab6e4896b3b270cc084905a9f2363","tid":2304049,"uid":225257,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"之後仲唱唔唱無盡？"},{"pid":"259d180e0c01d798d6d7675f0be05ee781c5e325","tid":2304049,"uid":59152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T01:0